Yes there are plans to repeat the surveys or Bulgarian participation in surveys:
-European School Survey Project on Alcohol and other Drugs - ESPAD. 
- European Health Interview Survey - EHIS;
- Global Youth Tobacco Survey - GYTS;
Since 2012 every year the National Statistical Institute is going to investigate the incidence of tobacco consumption.

